Perfect for kick-starting your day, apple, mango and spinach smoothie is the best option. The drink is packed with many important minerals, making it a great addition to your breakfast. Apples are an incredibly nutritious fruit that offers multiple health benefits. They are rich in fiber and antioxidants. Ingeredients Preparation Step 1 Add the mango, apple, yogurt, and honey to a blender. Top with approximately 1 cup of ice. Step 2 Fill the remainder of the blender with spinach, then blend until smooth and creamy. If you meet any resistance while blending, add water, a tablespoon at a time, until the ingredients blend smoothly. Step 3 Divide between two glasses, serve immediately and enjoy!